data.name: button9.ToolTip
data.value: Variable to create a stylish progress bar. The 'E' can be any emoji or string for text and represents the pointer. The 'L" is the length of the progressbar, a length of 13 is the max size for a line of the VRChat chatbox.

data.name: label122.ToolTip
data.value: When this toggle is enabled Windows Media Mode will not be initialized on program launch and will become unusable. Requires restarting the application. This setting may be used if you believe windows media mode may be causing crashing.
